                    "text": "  * cgroups: Disable memory resource controller by default. Allow it     to be enabled using kernel parameter 'cgroup_enable=memory'.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "[...]\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "  * cgroups: Enable CGROUP_MEM_RES_CTLR_SWAP but not\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
